name: Newjerseylinuxfest.org
body:
### New Jersey Linux Fest
New Jersey Linux Fest is a yearly festival that promotes the usage of Free/Libre Open Source Software, Knowledge, Hardware and Culture in NJ.

### Location
You are welcome to propose a location.

### Speakers
You are welcome to propose a talk.

### Donations
You are welcome to donate money to the conference.

### Cost
We will keep the cost as low as possible and not charge any entrance fee if possible.

### Schedule
None yet.
